{"ID":"20260424101859-1tnk1gw","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-1tnk1gw","title":"02_NPU全景与问题定义","type":"doc","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-44gaiqm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-44gaiqm","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"02 NPU全景与问题定义"}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-4yyfk77","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-4yyfk77","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果没有先把“为什么需要 NPU”讲清楚，后面所有微架构细节都会变成散点。因为 PE、脉动阵列、量化、编译器后端、runtime 都不是孤立优化，它们共同服务于同一个目标："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"在给定功耗、面积、成本、延迟约束下，把 AI 负载更高效地跑起来"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-b9c70n3","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-b9c70n3","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. NPU 不是为了“跑 AI”而生，而是为了在约束下跑 AI"}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-tq0qtoo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-tq0qtoo","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"把问题说完整，NPU 要解决的不是“能不能算”，而是："}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-jule4fs","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-jule4fs","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-ejbykc0","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-ejbykc0","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-60jtqdm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-60jtqdm","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"同样的 AI 工作负载，能不能在更低功耗下完成"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-hk1v49q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-hk1v49q","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-r72h5vt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-r72h5vt","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"同样的功耗和面积预算，能不能给出更高吞吐"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-r92xxau","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-r92xxau","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-3rpb0g3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-3rpb0g3","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"同样的系统约束，能不能把数据搬运压到更低"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-2kdwtjc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-2kdwtjc","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-za1v1n3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-za1v1n3","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"同样的模型，能不能用更可控的方式部署到边缘端、手机、汽车、数据中心"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-f27pqdg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-f27pqdg","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这就是 NPU 和“拿一个通用处理器硬跑模型”的根本区别。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-dwzpgup","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-dwzpgup","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CPU、GPU、FPGA 都能做 AI 计算，但它们的默认优化目标并不一样："}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-vt0c13m","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-vt0c13m","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-lwf936v","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-lwf936v","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-hm6mu57","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-hm6mu57","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CPU 优先保证广泛软件都能高效运行"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-zz2jnnr","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-zz2jnnr","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-u0umtho","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-u0umtho","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"GPU 优先保证大规模线程并行吞吐和编程生态"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-3u5eorh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-3u5eorh","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-nor9oin","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-nor9oin","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"FPGA 优先保证可重构和定制化"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-vjxpu7c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-vjxpu7c","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101859-9kygqg3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-9kygqg3","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"NPU 优先保证神经网络算子的"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"有效吞吐/能效/部署成本"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-niho92g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-niho92g","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所以 NPU 从第一天起就是一个带约束的专用解，而不是“更强的一般处理器”。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-w3aeykz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-w3aeykz","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"把四类处理器放在一张表里看，会更容易抓住 NPU 的问题定义："}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-s8ax72l","Type":"NodeTable","TableAligns":[0,0,0,0],"Properties":{"colgroup":"|||","id":"20260424101859-s8ax72l","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableHead","Data":"thead","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类型"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"默认优化目标"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"擅长什么"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"th","Children":[{"Type":"Nod