n":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是否能在目标模型和目标 batch 下给出足够吞吐与延迟"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"能效"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"每瓦能做多少有效工作，热和续航是否可接受"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"带宽压力"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"外存是否成为主要瓶颈，片上复用是否足够"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"面积与成本"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"阵列、SRAM、NoC、控制器、软件栈值不值得这部分硅预算"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"可编程性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"编译器与 runtime 是否能把真实模型稳定映射上去"}]}]},{"Type":"NodeTableRow","Data":"tr","Children":[{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"可集成性"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"Type":"NodeTableCell","Data":"td","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是否容易接入 SoC、驱动、框架、部署流程"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101859-72wqb4y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101859-72wqb4y","updated":"20260424101859"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这也是为什么任何只谈“TOPS”的 NPU 介绍都不完整。NPU 从来不是单指标问题，而是一个多约束折中问题。"}]},{"ID":"20260